n from the publisher. 0aPerformance artxThemes, motives. 0aEndurance art. 0aArts, Americany21st centuryxThemes, motives. 0aArt and religionzUnited StatesxHistoryy21st century. 4aElectronic books.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher. 0aTheater--text/theory/performance.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.8057432